data.description: Fantastic location!!  Tons of potential in this 3 bedroom 2 bath one-story home in a quiet North Arlington subdivision.  The home has a split bedroom floor plan with walk in closets in all bedrooms.   Large kitchen with stainless steel appliances, double ovens and a roomy breakfast room with dry bar.   Unique features include a 2nd living with a wet bar and enclosed patio that could be a game room, office, craft room or plant room.  Garage is two-car rear entry garage with a workbench and gated drive.  Close to AT&T stadium, Ranger Stadium, Six Flags,  and Hurricane Harbor.
